[Cite as 1/09/2004 Case Announcements #3, 2004-Ohio-88.]

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

January 9, 2004

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

1985-0007. State v. Williams.

Cuyahoga App. No. 47853. Upon consideration of appellant’s motion for stay of execution of death sentence scheduled for January 14, 2004,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion be, and hereby is, denied.
